    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;h2 id="dft-business-plan-other-key-data"&gt;DfT Business Plan other key data&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Geographical coverage: England&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Information broken down by: Region - data are available for London, English metropolitan areas (as a group), and English non-metropolitan areas (as a group)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="latest-data"&gt;Latest data&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In Quarter 3 (July – September) 2012, there were 1.16 billion passenger journeys on local buses in England.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
